{"tid":416846,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學生聞國歌肅立敬禮　網民盛讚校方德育好","createTime":"2017-09-28T06:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T06:38:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6886cc3396bc85cbc6bf459c72eedea709e82e","tid":416846,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00004/a577117c0017041ea7e7a68e27f140bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00004%2Fa577117c0017041ea7e7a68e27f140bc.jpg&h=48eaa18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地愈來愈重視愛國教育，甚至認為是德育最高標準，浙江寧波一間小學堪稱典範。有微博用戶上載照片，聲稱在校門外見證小學生們聽聞國歌響起時，全體立即止步敬禮。內地廣大網民轉發帖文盛讚，連中央電視台官方微博和新聞報道亦有提起此事。學校德育主任回應查詢，笑說學生們聽到國歌肅立敬禮已是學校老傳統，沒料會引起這麼大迴響。<br />\n<br />\n微博用戶「亮劍」星期二發布照片，大讚寧波四眼碶小學德育做得好。不出一天，這張相片成了內地網民熱話。照片下最熱門留言曰：「細節往往體現一個人的心性，所有學校都應該教育孩子，愛國從點點滴滴做起。」<br />\n<br />\n「亮劍」說照片是清晨送孩子上學時拍下。當時一班小學生陸陸續續返抵校園，忽然校內播起國歌，「感人的一幕出現了」，孩子們同時立正、面朝國旗敬禮，待國歌播完才繼續走。<br />\n<br />\n有網民初時還會質疑這幕是否經過刻意安排，內地傳媒於是派人到來了解。四眼碶小學德育主任吳曉丹老師透露，類似場景已是學校堅持多年的老傳統，周一到周五天天可見：「沒想到我們德育教育中的一個小細節，能得到這麼多網友認可。」<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，他們特別培育學生四「jing」（漢語拼音），亦即「敬、靜、淨、精」，其中「敬」是最高規範：「尊敬國旗需嚴肅，上學入校要敬禮，見到老師問聲好，客人來了熱相迎。」開學雖然只是兩星期，多得老師以身作則，加上高年級學生帶動，即使是一年級新生，聽到國歌時也會自覺停下腳步行禮。<br />\n<br />\n（央視網、新浪微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00004/a57a67fecaebc28bcf0f771b140b6d76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00004%2Fa57a67fecaebc28bcf0f771b140b6d76.jpg&h=add6fa02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00004/a57cb91596f421b1dd0be67bd7bede7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00004%2Fa57cb91596f421b1dd0be67bd7bede7d.jpg&h=7575fe23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00004/1506522744224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00004%2F1506522744224&d=1ko1tJ7vx4r8HpZMh5YTw04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=070badd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00004%2F1506522744224&h=e76ac632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00004/1506522744224</a>"},{"pid":"895f1fc453aadc7135d7a347828a5d98437fe637","tid":416846,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"支那人聽支那國歌停低好合理"},{"pid":"01a4228a38a0ef16abee532122ea05ded5cad9d4","tid":416846,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"祝佢地生生世世都留係支那呢個地獄啦"},{"pid":"5b5373bd9b3bd4606f2de01bece5965201be1716","tid":416846,"uid":68641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"時間停止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391227f7e523fc61d96073414f281b7bc7863f2b","tid":416846,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間停止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫日本拍套播國歌之後同條女扑野既av"},{"pid":"b54ba24b066d4ff0f839b261b1259e5e1b57f888","tid":416846,"uid":12404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sit!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5491b0d1885ed76705b40949a943d8eb829899ce","tid":416846,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:35:53.000Z","msg":"馬路黎個喎"},{"pid":"617a01cafaf9bf8d627a25b73c964e9